Package: wps-read-aloud-comate
Version: 1.2.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: ZHANG JING YAO <zhangjingyao@example.invalid>
Provides: wps-read-aloud
Description: WPS 文档朗读助手
 Developer: ZHANG JING YAO. Release date: 2026/05/26.
 Supports x64 银河麒麟系统, ARM64 银河麒麟系统, x64 UOS系统 and ARM64 UOS系统. Requires WPS Office 2019 for Linux or later; latest stable version is recommended.
 Provides a WPS JS add-in and local offline TTS daemon. The daemon listens
 only on 127.0.0.1 and uses a bundled Sherpa-onnx VITS fanchen-C Chinese
 model for clear offline read-aloud with lightweight English preprocessing.
